==Trivia==
*The smoke devil was first added to the game on [[26 January]] [[2005]] under the name '''Smokedevil''', described as "''The cave-dwelling cousin of the dust devils.''" Unlike the dust devil, it was not made accessible to players with the release of the [[Smoke Dungeon]].
*In ''RuneScape'', {{RSL|smoke devils}} are familiars that require a Summoning level of 61 to use. The smoke devil in ''Old School RuneScape'' shares the same model before {{RSL|Update:Patch Notes (22 July 2014)|its graphical update}} in 2014.

